data.description: Welcome to this beautiful one-story home located in the desirable area of Bulverde, TX. With four bedrooms and three bathrooms, this spacious house offers plenty of room for comfortable living. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow throughout the home, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. The master bedroom features a walk-in closet, providing ample storage space for all your belongings. Stay cool and comfortable year-round with ceiling fans in every room. The three-car garage offers plenty of space for parking and storage. This home is situated in a convenient location, close to schools, shopping, and dining options.
